228 ♦? Happiness Love for life is the fundamental ingredient of all recipes
for hap- piness. ...Happiness is the peak fulfillment of life. It is a
human’s own doing, his greatest power and liberty. Happiness is not
external to man, it is a genial force in him. It cannot be elsewhere.
